msgid ""
"This is the 1st release candidate of v0.9.2 for vLLM Ascend. Please follow "
"the [official doc](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/tree/v0.9.2rc1) to get started. From this release, V1 engine will be "
"enabled by default, there is no need to set `VLLM_USE_V1=1` any more. And "
"this release is the last version to support V0 engine, V0 code will be "
"cleaned up in the future."
msgstr ""
"这是 vLLM Ascend v0.9.2 的第一个候选发布版本。请遵循[官方文档](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-ascend/tree/v0.9.2rc1)开始使用。从本次发布起，V1 引擎将默认启用，不再需要设置 "
"`VLLM_USE_V1=1`。此外，该版本也是最后一个支持 V0 引擎的版本，V0 相关代码将在未来被清理。"

msgid ""
"**Full Changelog**: <https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
