"- 修复了前缀缓存中DeepSeek-V4压缩前缀查找的问题。[#10297](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/10297)\n"
"- 修复了GLM流式工具调用名称保留问题。[#10361](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/10361)\n"
"- 修复了vLLM v0.21.0下GLM5.1-W8A8 MTP加载权重错误。[#10317](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/10317)\n"
"- 将DeepSeek V4缓存钩子移入模型，移除了遗留的补丁环境变量。[#10327](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/10327) [#10333](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/10333)\n"
"- 修复了FP32 MM编码器注意力支持。[#10200](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/10200)\n"
"- 使vllm-ascend与上游vLLM单元测试预期保持一致。[#10146](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/10146)"

msgid ""
