"- **GDN Optimization**: Optimize GDN non-spec prefill fallback metadata ([#7756](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7756))\n"
"- **Qwen3-VL Support**: Support kv_rmsnorm_mrope for Qwen3-VL ([#7762](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/7762))\n"
