msgid ""
"- **MTP in PD Full graph**: Fixed support for ALL D-Nodes in full graph when running MTP in PD deployment. [#5472](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/5472)\n"
"- **DeepSeekV3.1 Accuracy**: Fixed DeepSeekV3.1 accuracy issue. [#6805](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/6805)\n"
