"- EPLB配置选项已移至[附加配置](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/user_guide/configuration/additional_config.html)中的`eplb_config`。旧选项在此版本中已移除。\n"
"- 分析器环境变量，如`VLLM_TORCH_PROFILER_DIR`和`VLLM_TORCH_PROFILER_WITH_PROFILE_MEMORY`，现在不适用于vLLM Ascend。请改用vLLM的`--profiler-config`参数。[#5928](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/pull/5928)"

